<h3>Evercam Play Version 1.1.2</h3> 

<ul>
	<li><b>- Sign in with either Email or Evercam username. digest authentication <br /></b></li>
	<li><b>- Support digest authentication.<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Add new camera to your Evercam account.<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Fill vendor/model details when create camera.<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Thumbnails for scanned cameras.<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Scan for cameras in your local network.<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Remove camera from your Evercam account<br/></b></li>
	<li><b>- Edit existing camera details.</b><br /></li>
</ul>
